data.description: Single story home with no HOA.  Lush, green front gated courtyard.  Large covered, screen-in patio in backyard, surrounded by grass.  Nice open floorplan with large living room, vaulted ceiling, window seat with storage, ceiling fan & light, and gas fireplace.  Kitchen has stainless steel appliances.  Ceiling fans and lights in bedrooms. Newer water heater and HVAC unit.  New entry door from garage and rolladen shutters in back.  Water conditioner included.  Interior repainted and new carpet and vinyl in hall bathroom replaced in November of 2023.
